</div>
<div>
<p>徽宗崇寧<measure quantity="2" unit="years">
<num value="2">二</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>詔<pc>：</pc>
<num value="6">六</num>尚局奉禦<pc>，</pc>今後許服金帶<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="4" unit="years">
<num value="4">四</num>年</measure>
